Unicode and ISO 10646
Unicode		 Unicode encodings in its latest version in logical group order
1 ISO-10646-UCS-Basic
UCS_Basic		 1993
ISO 10646 Basic plane 0x20-0x7E
IANA: ASCII subset of Unicode. Basic Latin = collection 1 See ISO 10646, Appendix A

2 ISO-10646-Unicode-Latin1
Unicode_Latin1		 1993
ISO 10646 Basic plane 0x20-0x7E plus Latin-1 Supplement plane 0xA0-0xFF
